sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Browser as Browser
    participant Theme as Theme Script
    participant Loader as Main JS
    participant Comp as Components
    participant Data as Data Layer
    participant Render as DOM Utils

    Note over Browser, Theme: 1. PRE-RENDER PHASE
    Browser->>Theme: Read localStorage
    Theme-->>Browser: Apply data-theme to HTML

    Note over Browser, Loader: 2. INITIALIZATION PHASE
    User->>Browser: Request Page
    Browser->>Loader: Fire DOMContentLoaded
    Loader->>Comp: Execute component scripts
    Comp-->>Browser: Inject SVGs and Layout
    Loader->>Comp: Sync Navigation Active Links
    Loader->>Comp: Sync Theme Toggle Icon UI

    Note over Browser, Data: 3. DATA AND RENDERING PHASE
    Loader->>Data: Import dataset arrays
    Loader->>Render: Pass Data and Template ID
    Render->>Browser: Locate template in DOM
    Render->>Render: Clone node and map data
    Render-->>Browser: Append elements to layout grid

    Note over Browser, Loader: 4. BEHAVIOR AND INTERACTION PHASE
    Loader->>Browser: Bind Theme Switcher events
    Loader->>Browser: Setup ScrollSpy Observers
    Loader->>Browser: Trigger ScrollReveal animations

    Note over User, Browser: 5. READY STATE
